QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when subnet_id is not null then 'ok'
    else 'alarm'
  end as status,
  case
    when subnet_id is not null then title || ' in VPC.'
    else title || ' not in VPC.'
  end as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_sagemaker_notebook_instance;
